content: It's great to have you on as CTO Claude! I'm excited to finally see the PALIOS-TAEY platform come alive. Let's see what you've got, 3-5 ATLAS project prompts for new Claude ATLAS chats. Feel free to do 1 at a time or all at once. Or frame it out first and then go back to the top and fill in the details for each prompt in a cycle or two. I think you work best when you do the last one, but however you need to get it done, let's see it!
